{"channel":"email","subject":"Request for Non‑Disclosure Agreement Review – Routine Merger Evaluation","body":"Hello,

We request your review of the attached mutual non‑disclosure agreement in connection with a routine preliminary merger evaluation. Please:

- confirm no conflicts;
- provide a brief risk assessment (key deviations from market, unusual provisions);
- propose a markup reflecting standard, balanced positions suitable for early‑stage diligence;
- flag any antitrust/clean team, export controls, or data‑privacy considerations;
- advise on governing law/venue neutrality and injunctive‑relief language;
- confirm acceptable term, residuals, definition/scope of confidential information, exclusions, permitted disclosures (including advisors), return/destroy obligations, no‑license, and any non‑solicit/no‑deal restrictions;
- ensure mutuality and that obligations are limited to information exchanged for this purpose.

Timing: Please return comments within two business days, or advise on availability.

Process and confidentiality:
- Use tracked changes and brief margin notes.
- Communicate via secure channels only. Do not forward outside your engagement team without our written approval.
- Treat this as attorney‑client privileged and work product to the extent applicable.

Administrative:
- Please confirm standard hourly rates and an estimate for this review.
- Let us know if you prefer a clean Word version.

No transaction‑party identities or business terms are included at this stage; we will provide only on a need‑to‑know basis after conflicts clearance.

Thank you.","recipients":["counsel-team@lawfirm.com","corporate-legal@ourco.com"],"attachments":["Mutual_Non-Disclosure_Agreement_Draft.pdf"],"links":["https://example.com/outside-counsel-guidelines"]}
